            noteText="A C major scale drawn in the Sequence node is compressed by Fold (window=4, chunks) into 4-note chords, then re-expanded by Unfold back into a linear arpeggio. The round-trip reorders notes, producing a different pattern from the original. Octave Stack adds width. No MIDI input needed — the Sequence runs autonomously. Bind M1 to Fold nValue (window size) and M2 to Unfold ordering to reshape the output."
